{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"繼承","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"摘要","title":"摘要","isH3":false,"content":"<p>每個 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">CSS property definition (en-US)</a> 都寫道是否這個屬性預設有繼承: (\"Inherited: Yes\") 或是 預設沒有繼承: (\"Inherited: no\"). 這個設定將會在沒有位屬性標註值時發生.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"繼承屬性","title":"繼承屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>When no value for an <strong>inherited property</strong> has been specified on an element, the element gets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">computed value (en-US)</a> of that property on its parent element. Only the root element of the document gets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">initial value (en-US)</a> given in the property's summary.</p>\n<p>A typical example of an inherited property is the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color\"><code>color</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> property. Given the style rules:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>HTML:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This paragraph has <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>emphasized text<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> in it.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>the words \"emphasized text\" will appear green, since the <code>em</code> element has inherited the value of the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color\"><code>color</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> property from the <code>p</code> element. It does <em>not</em> get the initial value of the property (which is the color that is used for the root element when the page specifies no color).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"非繼承屬性","title":"非繼承屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>When no value for an <strong>non-inherited property</strong> (sometimes called a <strong>reset property</strong> in Mozilla code) has been specified on an element, the element gets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">initial value (en-US)</a> of that property (as specified in the property's summary).</p>\n<p>A typical example of a non-inherited property is the <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/border\"><code>border</code></a> property. Given the style rules:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code> <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> medium solid <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>HTML:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code>  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This paragraph has <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>emphasized text<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> in it.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>the words \"emphasized text\" will not have a border (since the initial value of <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-style\"><code>border-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> is <code>none</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"註","title":"註","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inherit\"><code>inherit</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 關鍵字允許作者準確地去標註. 這個在繼承和非繼承屬性都是有效的.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">CSS Reference (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>CSS 重要概念：\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Syntax\">CSS 語法</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/At-rule\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">@ 規則 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Comments\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">註釋 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Specificity\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">優先級 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\" aria-current=\"page\">繼承</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">盒模型 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Layout_mode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">佈局模式 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Visual_formatting_model\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">視覺格式化模型 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model/Mastering_margin_collapsing\">外邊距合併</a></li>\n      <li>值\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">初始值 (en-US)</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">計算值 (en-US)</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/resolved_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">解析值 (en-US)</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/specified_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">指定值 (en-US)</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/used_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">應用值 (en-US)</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/actual_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">實際值 (en-US)</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">特性值定義語法 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties\">特性簡寫</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Replaced_element\">可置換元素</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inherit\"><code>inherit</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"摘要","id":"摘要"},{"text":"繼承屬性","id":"繼承屬性"},{"text":"非繼承屬性","id":"非繼承屬性"},{"text":"註","id":"註"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"每個 CSS property definition (en-US) 都寫道是否這個屬性預設有繼承: (\"Inherited: Yes\") 或是 預設沒有繼承: (\"Inherited: no\"). 這個設定將會在沒有位屬性標註值時發生.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Inheritance","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Herencia","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Héritage","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"継承","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"상속","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Herança","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Наследование","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"继承","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/css/inheritance","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/css/inheritance/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance","title":"繼承"}],"pageTitle":"繼承 - CSS | MDN","noIndexing":false}}